---
layout: base.njk
title: Hoteli u Banji Vrujci — Hotel Vrujci
description: "Hoteli u Banji Vrujci - Hotel Vrujci, jedini hotel u banji, sa termalnim bazenima."
permalink: /smestaj/hoteli/
activeNav: smestaj
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "Početna", url: "/" }
  - { label: "Smeštaj", url: "/smestaj" }
  - { label: "Hoteli", url: null }
---
<div class="container">
  <div class="page-head">
    <div class="eyebrow">Smeštaj · Banja Vrujci</div>
    <h1>Hoteli u Banji Vrujci</h1>
    <p>Hotel Vrujci je jedini hotel u banji — sportsko-rekreativni kompleks sa termalnim bazenima i lekovitom vodom.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="listing-grid" id="listingGrid" style="padding-top:0;">
    {% for item in collections.hoteli %}
    <a class="list-card" data-name="{{ item.data.title }}" href="{{ item.url | noslash }}">
      <div class="lc-thumb">
        {% if item.data.slike and item.data.slike[0] %}
        <img src="{{ item.data.slike[0] }}" alt="{{ item.data.title }}" onerror="this.style.opacity=0">
        {% else %}
        <div class="ph-thumb"><span class="ph-mono">{{ item.data.title | first }}</span><span class="ph-label">Foto u pripremi</span></div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="lc-body">
        <h3>{{ item.data.title }}</h3>
        {% if item.data.subtitle %}<p>{{ item.data.subtitle }}</p>{% endif %}
        <div class="lc-footer">
          <span class="lc-call">📞 {{ item.data.telefon or "Pozovite za broj" }}</span>
          <span class="lc-link">Detalji →</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
